    4807 [label="SPDXLicense:\nThis license takes effect 13 May, 2015. The changes from the previous version\nmake clear that the license is applicable to both software and text, by changing\nthe name and substituting \"work\" for instances of \"software and its\ndocumentation.\" It moves \"notice of changes or modifications to the files\" to\nthe copyright notice, to make clear that the license is compatible with other\nliberal licenses. In 2023, W3C made minor modifications to this license as of\nJan 1, 2023 (see URL above). However, those changes did not give rise to a new\nlicense under the SPDX Matching Guidelines, thus the same id can be used."
         ,fillcolor="beige;1"
         ,shape=plaintext];
